La Vierge de Denchawi, c'est la fille d'Hassan Mahfooz, un condamné à mort;
                        elle a nom Setel-Dar et, c'est là le point capital de l'action, elle est
                        fiancée à Mohamed-el-Abd un des accusés remis en liberté.

Sold in Egypt by all chemists at Fr. 3.50 the box cr Fr. 17.50 for six boxes;
                        also the depôts of S. Fischer & Cie and Galetti & Figli,
                        Alexandria.

6th-On being admitted, candidates must sign an engagement that they will work
                        either in Upper or Lower Egypt during the whole or part of their service, as
                        I may be ordered by the Administration;

7th-Popils will receive P.T. 7 per day each during the period allowed for
                        studying telegraphy and will receive higher pay when they have the telegraph
                        certicate when they will be absorbed in the staff of the station;
